articles.title: About this site
articles.description: Some additional details about this project
articles.contents:
About Me
I’m Mahima Malhotra, an incoming freshman at Purdue University. I’m planning on double majoring in Computer Science and Data Science.
Sources
The first source was Primer.Data (Kane 2020)
The source for the data was the U.S. Chronic Disease Indicators (CDI) (CDC 2021) from the CDC, which collected data from numerous organizations.



CDC. 2021. “U.s. Chronic Disease Indicators (CDI).”


Kane, David. 2020. Primer.data.
